              </p>
              <h3 class="heading-tertiary u-margin-bottom-small">Digital Excellence</h3>
              <p class="paragraph">
                The quality of our digital learning courses is paramount. This is why we developed a special structure for all our online offers: The three track structure.  
              </p>
              
              <a class="btn-text" href="#programs">See our online courses &rarr;</a>
              
              
